<div><head>王歆孝子傳</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1329_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1329_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1329_CHANT_001-1a.2">王歆孝子傳<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1329_CHANT_001-1a.3">竺彌，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1329_CHANT_001-1a.4">字道綸。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1329_CHANT_001-1a.5">父生時畏雷，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1329_CHANT_001-1a.6">每至天陰，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1329_CHANT_001-1a.7">輒馳至墓，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1329_CHANT_001-1a.8">伏墳哭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1329_CHANT_001-1a.9">有白兔在其左右。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1329_CHANT_001-1a.10">《御覽》十三。<lb/></seg>
</p>
